The shown label example for #2 is only one option, you could also use a simple loop:<p><pre><code>    for loop := true; loop; {
        select {
        case <-time.After(time.Second):
            fmt.Println(&quot;hello&quot;)
        default:
            loop = false
        }
    }
    fmt.Println(&quot;ending&quot;)</code></pre>

